      "layout": "The page primarily uses a max-width contained layout, with content sitting within a central column. The hero section features a prominent, left-aligned headline and text block, paired with a grid of product images on the right. Subsequent sections often employ an alternating text-left/visual-right pattern. Vertical spacing between sections is generous and consistent. Some sections use `Sky Blue` (#ecf2ff) or `Pale Peach` (#fff4ec) backgrounds to create visual breaks. Navigation is a sticky top bar with brand logo left and text links and an outlined button on the right.",
